mixin CafeContact
  +Section#cafeContact
    .row.justify-content-center.mb-lg-6(data-zanim-timeline!={} data-zanim-trigger="scroll")
      .col-md-10.col-lg-7.col-xl-6.text-center
        h2.text-decoration-underline.mb-4.fs-6.fs-sm-5 this way to sparrow
        p.mb-4 If you want to give your event a touch of sparrow, connect directly with us today and let's co-create something delightful for you.
